Sampdoria are hoping to complete the signing of Everton forward Samuel Eto'o on Tuesday.

The Genoa outfit has been in talks with Everton and Eto'o's representatives in recent weeks with a view to completing the move for the 33-year-old.

'Eto'o should be here in Genoa on Tuesday,' Samp sporting director Carlo Osti told Italian TV station Telenord.

